name: Gone Bananas 2.0
description: This is a Basic Banana, don’t be fooled, Everyone is going nanas for bananas. All of our virtual bananas are immensely valuable as game pieces within our NFT real live virtual reality crossover game “Gone Bananas” Collect as many bananas as you can and redeem them for access to future events and airdrops. This Bananas was created by daniel123ayala and remixed by Alexander Mazzei and Kostas Massios
